headline: Toymaker Hasbro joins wave of companies suing U.S. government over IEEPA tariff payments
summary: NEW YORK, NY, Feb 27 - Toymaker Hasbro on Friday joined ‌hundreds of companies suing for refunds ‌of tariffs paid under President Donald Trump’s emergency ​trade measures, which were deemed illegal by the U. Supreme Court last week, according to court documents.
